  "keyFeatures": [
    "High-performance LLM inference on NVIDIA GPUs",
    "Advanced quantization (FP8, FP4, INT4, AWQ, SmoothQuant)",
    "Speculative decoding for throughput optimization",
    "Paged KV cache and inflight batching",
    "Custom optimized attention kernels",
    "Multi-GPU and multi-node distributed inference",
    "OpenAI-compatible server (trtllm-serve)",
    "Python LLM API for easy integration",
    "Support for 80+ model architectures",
    "PyTorch and TensorRT backends",
    "LoRA adapter support",
    "Multimodal model support"
